Package: zimagent
Version: 1.0.0
Section: education
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: python3 (>= 3.9), python3-pyqt5, python3-psutil
Maintainer: ZimAgent <hello@zimagent.local>
Description: ZimAgent Desktop
 Offline CRUD + semantic search desktop application
 for Wikipedia ZIM archives.
 .
 Features:
  * Read, write, edit and delete ZIM articles
  * Semantic search powered by TurboRag
  * Local LLM question answering
  * MCP server for Claude Desktop / LangChain integration
  * Fully offline – no internet required
